snippet.title: Winds Up Kitesurfing | PC Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Play on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2799240/Winds_Up_Kitesurfing/
Play on Android! 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.TooMoose.WindsUpKitesurfing
Play on IOS!
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/winds-up-kitesurfing/id6470040852

Get ready for the PC version of Winds Up Kitesurfing. 
I have been working hard getting the controls sorted so you can play with keyboard or gamepad (preferred). Also a new location has been added!

Music from #Uppbeat (free for Creators!):
https://uppbeat.io/t/hartzmann/paradise-island
License code: PTJOTFQBIAV8D3Z4

#WindsUpKitesurfing #MobileGaming #KitesurfingGame #kitesurfing
